Definition: in an indulgent manner
Example: I was indulgently advised to give the kids what they wanted unless I wished my son to be socially ostracised
Synonyms: adj, all, permissive, indulgent, in, an, manner, I, was, advised, to, give, the, kids, what, they, wanted, unless, wished, my, son, be, socially, ostracised
Category: adv.all
